Package src.product

Class Product

  • java.lang.Object
    • src.product.Product
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Product>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Book, Clothes, Drink, Electronic, Food, Furniture, PersonalCare, Toy
    public class Product
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Product>
    A general Comparable Product class which can be extended for various kind of Products.
